ontext2D/createConicGradient\"><code>createConicGradient()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/createImageData\"><code>createImageData()</code></a></li><li><em><code>createLinearGradient()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/createPattern\"><code>createPattern()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/createRadialGradient\"><code>createRadialGradient()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/drawFocusIfNeeded\"><code>drawFocusIfNeeded()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/drawImage\"><code>drawImage()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/drawWidgetAsOnScreen\"><code>drawWidgetAsOnScreen()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/drawWindow\"><code>drawWindow()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/ellipse\"><code>ellipse()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/fill\"><code>fill()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/fillRect\"><code>fillRect()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/fillText\"><code>fillText()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/getContextAttributes\"><code>getContextAttributes()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/getImageData\"><code>getImageData()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/getLineDash\"><code>getLineDash()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/getTransform\"><code>getTransform()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/isPointInPath\"><code>isPointInPath()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/isPointInStroke\"><code>isPointInStroke()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/lineTo\"><code>lineTo()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/measureText\"><code>measureText()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/moveTo\"><code>moveTo()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/putImageData\"><code>putImageData()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/quadraticCurveTo\"><code>quadraticCurveTo()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/rect\"><code>rect()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/resetTransform\"><code>resetTransform()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/restore\"><code>restore()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/rotate\"><code>rotate()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/save\"><code>save()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/scale\"><code>scale()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/scrollPathIntoView\"><code>scrollPathIntoView()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/setLineDash\"><code>setLineDash()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/setTransform\"><code>setTransform()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/stroke\"><code>stroke()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/strokeRect\"><code>strokeRect()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/strokeText\"><code>strokeText()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/transform\"><code>transform()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/translate\"><code>translate()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><code><strong>CanvasRenderingContext2D</strong></code><strong><code>.createLinearGradient()</code></strong>方法创建一个沿参数坐标指定的直线的渐变。</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/createLinearGradient/mdn-canvas-lineargradient.png\" width=\"264\" height=\"121\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n\n<p>该方法返回一个线性 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient\"><code>CanvasGradient</code></a>对象。想要应用这个渐变，需要把这个返回值赋值给&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/fillStyle\" title=\"fillStyle\"><code>fillStyle</code></a> 或者&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/strokeStyle\" title=\"strokeStyle\"><code>strokeStyle</code></a>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">CanvasGradient <var><em>ctx</em>.createLinearGradient(x0, y0, x1, y1);</var>\n</pre>\n\n<p><code>createLinearGradient()</code> 方法需要指定四个参数，分别表示渐变线段的开始和结束点。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"x0\"><code>x0</code></dt>\n <dd>起点的 x 轴坐标。</dd>\n <dt id=\"y0\"><code>y0</code></dt>\n <dd>起点的 y&nbsp;轴坐标。</dd>\n <dt id=\"x1\"><code>x1</code></dt>\n <dd>终点的 x 轴坐标。</dd>\n <dt id=\"y1\"><code>y1</code></dt>\n <dd>终点的 y&nbsp;轴坐标。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"canvasgradient\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient\"><code>CanvasGradient</code></a></dt>\n <dd>一个根据指定线路初始化的线性<code>&nbsp;</code><code>CanvasGradient</code> 对象。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用线性渐变填充一个矩形","title":"使用线性渐变填充一个矩形","isH3":true,"content":"<p>这个例子使用<code>createLinearGradient()</code>&nbsp;方法初始化了一个线性渐变。在这个线性渐变中添加了三种色彩。最后，这个渐变被赋值给上下文对应的属性，实现了对矩形的填充。</p>\n\n<h4 id=\"html\">HTML</h4>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>canvas</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>canvas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<h4 id=\"javascript\">JavaScript</h4>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">var canvas = document.getElementById('canvas');\nvar ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');\n\n// Create a linear gradient\n// The start gradient point is at x=20, y=0\n// The end gradient point is at x=220, y=0\nvar gradient = ctx.createLinearGradient(20,0, 220,0);\n\n// Add three color stops\ngradient.addColorStop(0, 'green');\ngradient.addColorStop(.5, 'cyan');\ngradient.addColorStop(1, 'green');\n\n// Set the fill style and draw a rectangle\nctx.fillStyle = gradient;\nctx.fillRect(20, 20, 200, 100);</pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"结果\">结果</h4>\n\n\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"结果\" id=\"frame_filling_a_rectangle_with_a_linear_gradient\" width=\"700\" height=\"180\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/createLinearGradient/_sample_.filling_a_rectangle_with_a_linear_gradient.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范描述","id":"规范描述","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/canvas.html#dom-context-2d-createlineargradient-dev","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.CanvasRenderingContext2D.createLinearGradient"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.CanvasRenderingContext2D.createLinearGradient","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/createLinearGradient/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko特性说明","title":"Gecko 特性说明","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>自&nbsp;Gecko 2.0&nbsp;(Firefox 4 / Thunderbird 3.3 / SeaMonkey 2.1)开始，参数指定了极值会抛出<code>NOT_SUPPORTED_ERR</code>&nbsp; 而不再是之前的&nbsp;<code>SYNTAX_ERR </code>异常。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"<br>\n 参见","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"compat-mobile\"></div>\n\n<ul>\n <li>接口定义：&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/createRadialGradient\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D.createRadialGradient()</code></a></li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"\n 参见"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范描述","id":"规范描述"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"<br>\n 参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.createLinearGradient()方法创建一个沿参数坐标指定的直线的渐变。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.createLinearGradient()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.createLinearGradient()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.createLinearGradient()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/canvasrenderingcontext2d/createlineargradient","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/canvasrenderingcontext2d/createlineargradient/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D","title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/createLinearGradient","title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.createLinearGradient()"}],"pageTitle":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.createLinearGradient() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}